node.detail_zh: 患者有長期病患，2019 年 10 月 26 日到巴基斯坦，2020 年 7 月 3 日乘搭阿聯酋航空 EK380 回港，抵港後入住檢疫中心，沒有病徵。
node.detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions, travelled to Pakistan on October 26, 2019, and returned to Hong Kong by flight EK380 on July 3, 2020. She was transferred to quarantine centre and exhibited no symptoms.
